Assassins Of Revenge | Full Movie | Classic Action Movie | Leslie Nielsen

Although primarily known today for his comic roles, Leslie Nielsen used to excel as the heavy. In this intense action feature, he stars as Jonathan Trevor, an American agent who defects and finds himself hunted by a group of drug-fueled hit-men and his former partner Frank Lassiter (Gary Lockwood), in the sleazy underbelly of the Philippines.
